                <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:Arial">• Statements and Consent</span></p>
                
                <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:Arial">• Changes to this Privacy
                Policy</span></p>
                
                <p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family:Arial">• Contact us</span></p>
                
