                <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:
                normal"><span style="font-family:Arial">Collection of Personal Information</span></b></p>
                
                <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial">When
                you become a '.$brand.' application user, you are required to provide certain
                information so that you can use our services. We will collect your personal
                information when you register and periodically update it when using the '.$brand.'
                application service. The information we collect includes name, identification
                number, address, mobile number, email address, place and date of birth, gender.
                When you use our application, we will process technical data such as the amount
                in the balance statement application on your '.$brand.' application.</span></p>
                
                <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:
                normal"><span style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></b></p>
                
                <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:
                normal"><span style="font-family:Arial">Use of Personal Information</span></b></p>
                
