                personal information we collect can be used to facilitate the use of services,
                verify account ownership, confirm conditions related to services, provide
                information about new features and more. We will use your name, mobile number
                and e-mail address to send messages regarding application updates, promotional
                programs and password change / update information. We will use your bank
                account information for various purposes related to financial balances on your
                '.$brand.' application. From time to time we may use your personal information to
                conduct research and distribute questionnaires in order to improve service
                quality. Personal Information is used in an anonymous form and as a whole to
                closely monitor which features of the service are used most frequently, to
                analyze usage patterns and to focus on improving our services. Images or photos
                uploaded in the '.$brand.' application will be used for data verification
                materials or other purposes if necessary for '.$brand.'\'s internal interests. We
                use technical data in the form of IMEI and WIFI MAC Address to ensure a device
                has been verified. Our system will automatically send a verification code</span></p>
                
                <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
                
                <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial">in
