                mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family:Arial;
                mso-fareast-font-family:Arial"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">•<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:Arial">We state that we are not involved in the business of
                selling and buying your personal information to third parties.</span></p>
                
                <p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;
                mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1"><span style="font-family:Arial;
                mso-fareast-font-family:Arial"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">•<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-family:Arial">We can provide your information to the PPATK as an
                independent government agency formed for the Prevention and Eradication of the
                Crime of Money Laundering which has the task of preventing and eradicating the
                crime of money laundering. As stipulated in Article 39 of Law Number 8 Year
                2010. This institution has the authority to implement policies on the
                prevention and eradication of money laundering as well as establishing an
