                <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
                
                <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:
                normal"><span style="font-family:Arial">Updating of Personal Information</span></b></p>
                
                <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial">You
                can update your personal information anytime by accessing the profile feature
                that we provide. We take steps to share updates to your personal information
                with third parties and our affiliates if your personal information is still
                required for the above purposes.</span></p>
                
                <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
                
                <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:
                normal"><span style="font-family:Arial">Personal Information Security</span></b></p>
                
                <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial">We
                try to protect the personal information you provide with the database security
                system standards that we use, and we also keep your personal information from
                being used by unknown parties. You may not reveal your security password to
                anyone if you do, so if an error occurs, it is not the responsibility of
                '.$brand.', then the responsibility of the customer.</span></p>
                
                <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
                
                <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:
                normal"><span style="font-family:Arial">Statements and Consent</span></b></p>
                
                <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial">By
                using the '.$brand.' application, you declare yourself that you have read and
                fully understood this Privacy Policy. You also acknowledge that you give us the
                right to use and share your personal information with third parties for a
                reasonable reason to the extent permitted by applicable legal provisions. You
                agree not to make any claims against '.$brand.' in terms of disclosing your
