                Jurisdiction of the West Jakarta Class IA District Court.</span></p>
                
                <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial">&nbsp;</span></p>
                
                <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:
                normal"><span style="font-family:Arial">Changes to this Privacy Policy</span></b></p>
                
                <p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Arial">PT.
